English: A group of Jacobites calling themselves the Sans Culottes have occupied Nouvelle Orleans and are spreading dangerous ideas throughout the nation.
We have finally defeated the Christians of Iberia and have secured our glorious Caliphate a bright future.

Asturias, the bastion of Christianity in the Iberian Peninsula has finally been overwhelmed by the Moors. With this Millenia-spanning kingdom now laid to rubble, its inhabitants find themselves living in Al Andalus, the very enemy they had sought to destroy for even longer than the kingdom's lifespan, as such, many of them are now trying to leave for Elisio, a Catholic state founded by Iberians living under Al Andalus, mainly from the West coast of the Caliphate of Cordoba.

Alberto Barbosa is a name commonly used to represent a nondescript man from Portugal among users on 4chan's /int/ (international) board. The phrase "t. Alberto Barbosa" is often placed alongside a photoshopped illustration of an African man from the Age of Empires II expansion The African Kingdoms with a Portuguese flag on his turban, mocking the inclusion of Portugal in the game. Additionally, the character is often referenced in the context of We Wuz Kings jokes on the image board.
The True Masters of the Coast

With the lands dirrectly administered by us having vastly expanded, it is only natural that peoples with different cultures are now within our empire. We have to adress this situation and choose how we want to deal with them.
After mass riots in our capital, Persian nationalists stormed the government building and demanded that the Mongol Government be replaced with a new Persian-focsed government.
Intellectuals and Men of Science in Bucharest, especially young ones, sent to study abroad, are trying to modernize the Romanian state to be more in line with other civilized nations.

Rajputana has been in decline, ever since the Oirat invasion of India, a problem that's made even worse, as 2 notable foreign powers have established significant presences on the continent. We have managed to somewhat keep a technological edge over our fellow Indians however.

Ethiopia as of now is fairly decentralized, with regional autonomy, due to the rights of our vassals. Revoking these rights would bring us more prosperity, but it would also anger some under the rule of these vassals, including said vassals. Thankfully, our superiour technology, granted to us by the Crusaders in Jerusalem, due to our efforts to help them in their efforts to spread christianity, allows us to unite these lands without much of a hassle.
Following the population of Central America with mostly German speaking africans, they increasingly feel as if their national identity is different from that of their Metropole, which is to say us.

You forgot your pills again! You just woke up in a strange world where Hyperborean Byzantium is real and the Mongol empire did a large amount of trolling, Poland is very epic and the Italians colonized the Americas.

Legiuirea pentru emanciparea tuturor țiganilor din Principatul Țării Românești, or the act of emancipation of all gypsies of Wallachia was an act issued by the Wallachian government that made all gypsies free from slavery/serfdom.
Following the mass riots in Munich,said rioters have almost encircled the Royal residence and are demanding more rights.
The South Slavs have existed in our lands for centuries,yet not as long as us, even so, we should allow them some forms of representation to appease them.
Taking this decision will lock you out of the "Unite the Peninsula" decision

After many centuries of separation, it has become clear that even with out religious differences, we are not so different, sharing many customs. Even our languages are mostly the same, bar the arabs in the south, both of them stem from Latin and are very closely related. It is thus fitting that we attempt to unite under one, even with innevitable bloodshed. (Taking this decision will lock you out of the Caliphate Path of Al Andalus)

The Failure of the Emperor in 1834 to defend Crete against the Italian states was catastrophic, humiliating the empire and himself. This lead to the themes of the empire to rise up against him, proclaiming themselves as the new emperors, or in some cases, the populace overthrew their noble leaders and replaced them with republics, which is what these themes would do to the empire. Our strong position allows us to reunite the Empire once again, like a phoenix from the ashes.

Discovered by Dutch explorers, Tasmania is relatively low populated, being one of our most recently acquired colonial holdings. Reforming the administration and attracting immigrants to the colony might help us in the long run, especially since it would be quite likely that the new semi-independent colony would ask for reintegration.
We will support our Cossacks in colonizing Siberia with grain and cattle. This decision applies to provinces you own in Siberia, the more you have the more valuable it is.

Russian Empire government ministers personally appointed by the Emperor Alexander III of Russia and by his son, the Tsarevich Nicholas (later Emperor Nicholas II from 1894), supervised the building of the railway between 1891 and 1916. Even before its completion, the line attracted travelers who wrote of their adventures.The Trans-Siberian Railway has directly connected Moscow with Vladivostok since 1916.

While the province of Dacia exists in name and posesses some Dacian territories, the most important one of all, Transylvania, the homeland of the Dacians is not one of them. When we do recapture said provinces, we will be able to move our capital there once more.
Reforming the colonial governmnet of Nye Zealand will allow better management of the territory.

The leaders of Morea approached us with a very one-sided proposal, which is to say, one-sided for us. The leaders of the Morean revolt, being Orthodox clergymen see it fit that their country with its Greek heritage, be incorporated into the Byzantine Empire.
Our Greek Brothers call for our aid!
The Parthenopaean Republic, uncontent with our rule over Southern Italy has risen up!
Kaiser Louis, our beloved emperor has passed into the afterlife. May God rest his soul.
The people are calling for reform, some, horrificly are even calling for the monarchy to be abolished entirely!
Protestant teachings say that if a child works instead of going to sunday school, then they will turn into a catholic.
With India in the claws of other powers, we must set our sights on China!

A series of unfortunate events have lead to the Protestant population to despise our monarch and some are even calling for it to be overthrown and replaced with a republic! However, it is worth noting that the mostly catholic Scottish and Irish still support House Stuart, if we are to give into the rebels' demands we would anger them quite a lot.
The population in this province is coping and ,quite possibly, seething at their loss.

The Latin language has for long lived as ceremonial language in religious affairs, but now we strive to have the language implemented in all facets of society. This will be long and arduous, but it must be done if we want to call ourselves Romans.
Our society has finally started to show signs of adoption and adaptation of Latin in day to day life, but this is still far from universal and we must keep integrating this language more and more.

We have for long vyed to have dominion over Albion at the expense of the Irish. After finally pushing them out of Britannia proper, it is time to invade Ierne and finally unify the celts under one flag.

The Scots have long been a rebellious people who have caused us much trouble over the history of the Emerald Island. Ierne has long endured these hardships, but we cannot tolerate this any longer. It is time to push into the heartland of the Scots.

The Scots have been increasing their threats of war for the rest of Britannia and Wales, we must no longer sit by idly stand by and watch as they encroach upon our territory. Britannia cannot remain as the Status Quo is, it must be under our direct rule.

For many centuries we have co-existed with various different tribes. These all have a culture and history that is ancestral to this land and we need to put the status of tribe behind us and unite as one.

The Pas-de-Calais has long been appropriated by the Dutch, they have gone to many lengths to try to remove the French influence in the Picard language, but their efforts were not enough. Our deep cultural ties with the Picard are still visible to this day, we will teach the Picards to be part of our culture once again.
